reviews.title: Fantastic service from hassle free lender
reviews.body: The application process is straightforward, and similar to those required by other online lenders. However,  jacaranda loans' application form is faster to fill out than most because they do not require an extensive breakdown of your living expenses. This takes some of the stress and tedium out of filling out the initial application. The response to my application was as prompt as the website claims, and the staff who subsequently contacted me were pleasant, professional and concise. Funds were received on the same day, as promised. The only criticism i have is of the opening page of the website where the drop down menu suggests that the applicant can choose the time frame over which their loan is repaid. I was a little disappointed to find that the lending period offered was about half the time i had entered, which raised the repayments above the value i had been expecting. Otherwise jacaranda loans have been the fastest responding team with the fairest terms  of all the online loans companies i have dealt with.
